[ 2026-03-05 16:46:28,779 ] 99 root - INFO - Search Results:[{'score': 0.84465444, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_108', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '## What do you need?\n\nIncorporation/Registration Certificate\n\nDirector details\n\nProof of concept like pitch deck/website link/video (in case of a validation/\n\nearly traction/scaling stage startup) respectively\n\nPatent and trademark details (Optional)\n\nPAN Number', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 108}, {'score': 0.83756876, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_81', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '## Your profile details have been successfully recorded.\n\nYou may also consider getting Startup recognition, a process by which Department of Industrial Policy and Promotion recognizes you as a Startup. A startup recognition allows one to avail a host of benefits put in place by DIPP specially for Startups. These include self certification of certain environment and labor laws, access to taking part in government procurement, patent support and more.\n\nTo get recognized, simply click on the Get Recognized button\nand furnish some additional information which the form asks\nfor. Ensure you enter essential information like Incorporation\nnumber and entity type to apply for recognition.\n\nGo to Dashboard', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 81}, {'score': 0.83458316, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_106', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '*The image displays a digital screenshot of a "STARTUP RECOGNITION FORM" interface, likely from a web-based application. The form is titled "Entity Details" and is numbered "1". It contains several fields with red asterisks indicating mandatory information. The fields are: "Nature of Entity" (with a dropdown menu set to "Select"), "Industry" (with a dropdown menu set to "Select"), "Sector" (with a dropdown menu set to "Select"), "Categories" (with a dropdown menu set to "Select"), "Company Incorporation Number(CIN)" (a text input field), and "Name of the Entity" (a text input field). A note at the top advises that changes to auto-filled fields should be made in the profile settings and to click the save button for specific sections. The background features a geometric, abstract design', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 106}, {'score': 0.8315209, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_86', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '## Recognition Application Detail\n\nUser Details\n\nName\n\nCompany Name\n\nRecognition Form Status\n\nCurrent Status\n\nApplication', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 86}, {'score': 0.8291197, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_6', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '## Intellectual Property Rights (IPR)\n\nTo promote awareness and adoption of IPRs by Startups and facilitate them in protecting and commercialising the IPRs, Startup India provides access to high quality Intellectual Property services and resources, including:\n\nFast-tracking of Startup patent applications: The patent application of Startups is fast-tracked for examination and disposal. The process is much faster for recognised Startups.', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 6}]
