[ 2026-03-05 16:46:45,886 ] 99 root - INFO - Search Results:[{'score': 0.85035086, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_114', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '---\n\nGlossary\n\nAccelerator: An accelerator is typically a 3-4 month program for Startups at early traction and scaling stage. It is a process of intense, rapid and immersive education aimed at accelerating the growth of the Startup. The accelerator may take a set amount of seed equity from the Startups in their cohorts in exchange for capital and mentorship.\n\nAngel Group: An angel group is a network of angel investors who invest collectively in small Startups or entrepreneurs. They typically invest in angel, seed, and sometimes Series A rounds.\n\nAngel: Angel rounds are the first round that a company may go through. Angel investors, friends, and/or family may invest in an angel round to get a new company off the ground.', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 114}, {'score': 0.82359946, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_115', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': 'Convertible Note: It is a loan where an investor provides cash to a Startup company, and the investor gets an option to convert the debt to equity in the company.\n\nCo-Working Space: A co-working space is a company that provides a shared working environment for teams working typically for different employees, in the same office. No equity is taken from companies by the co-working space.\n\nIncubator: An incubator is a workspace created to offer early-stage Startups access to all resources they need under one roof. They provide office space, mentoring, business services, funding, and networking opportunities to the incubatees.', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 115}, {'score': 0.80884695, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_79', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': 'established business." A "Individual" card (pink icon with a person) describing someone "Aspiring entrepreneur, Regular freelancer." A "Enabler" card (purple icon with a house) describing someone "Help grow the startup ecosystem. Share your Expertise here."*', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 79}, {'score': 0.805225, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_84', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '2.  **Top Right (Active/Upcoming Programs):** A white section titled "Active/Upcoming Programs" lists two items. The first is a yellow graphic for "SUVNIK INCUBATION 20..." with a date of "30 SEP 2019" and a description: "We at Suvnik Incubation Services, are building Silgun\'s first startup...". The second is a graphic for "JILL IDEAS - India\'s Biggest PropTech Innovation Challenge in partnership..." with the same date and description.', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 84}, {'score': 0.7947404, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_67', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '*The image provided is a QR code, not a text document. Therefore, there is no text to transcribe.*\n\nFor any queries please call us on 1800115565 or drop us an email at dipp-startups@nic.in\n\n---', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 67}]
