-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_6', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '## Intellectual Property Rights (IPR)\n\nTo promote awareness and adoption of IPRs by Startups and facilitate them in protecting and commercialising the IPRs, Startup India provides access to high quality Intellectual Property services and resources, including:\n\nFast-tracking of Startup patent applications: The patent application of Startups is fast-tracked for examination and disposal. The process is much faster for recognised Startups.', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 6}, {'score': 0.832085, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_8', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': 'Want to protect your innovative idea? Scan the QR code below\nto contact the IPR facilitators.', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 8}, {'score': 0.8124984, 'chunk_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262_4', 'doc_id': 'cb9ced74-4c20-4be6-94fe-c025ca10a262', 'content': '## Resources\n\nLearning and Development Programs – Step-by-step guide to starting a business in India\n\nGovernment Schemes – Centralized repository of all Government schemes for the Startup Ecosystem Actors\n\nState Startup Policies – Single point to access all notified Startup Policies by the respective State Governments\n\nPro Bono Services – Get free applications, cloud credits, legal and banking support from our partners\n\nKnowledge Bank – A quick walkthrough on all things Startup, including company registration, investor engagement, legal considerations etc.\n\nTools and Templates – A repository of sample templates for all legal & HR documents, investor decks, deeds, contracts etc.\n\nNetworking – Connect with people from the Startup Ecosystem on the portal', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 4}]
